        "### Model Download List & Locations\n\n| Input / Type | Filename | Direct Download Link | ComfyUI Target Folder |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| **base_model** | `ltx-2.3-22b-dev-fp8.safetensors` | [Download (FP8)](https://huggingface.co/Hippotes/LTX-2.3-various-formats/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-22b-dev-fp8.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/` |\n| **lora** | `ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-lora-384-1.1.safetensors` | [Download (LoRA)](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-2.3/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-lora-384-1.1.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/loras/` |\n| **clip_1** | `gemma-3-12b-it-heretic-v2_int8.safetensors` | [Download (INT8)](https://huggingface.co/DreamFast/gemma-3-12b-it-heretic-v2/resolve/main/comfyui/gemma-3-12b-it-heretic-v2_int8.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/` |\n| **clip_2** | `ltx-2.3_text_projection_bf16.safetensors` | [Download (BF16)](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/resolve/main/text_encoders/ltx-2.3_text_projection_bf16.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/` |\n| **vae** | `LTX23_video_vae_bf16.safetensors` | [Download (BF16)](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/resolve/main/vae/LTX23_video_vae_bf16.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/vae/` |\n| **audio_vae** | `LTX23_audio_vae_bf16.safetensors` | [Download (BF16)](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/LTX2.3_comfy/resolve/main/vae/LTX23_audio_vae_bf16.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/vae/` |\n| **upscale_model** | `ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors` | [Download (x2 v1.1)](https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-2.3/resolve/main/ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors) | `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models/` |\n\n---\n\n### Model Installation:\nPlease download the required `.safetensors` files using the direct links and move them into the corresponding ComfyUI subdirectories. Make sure the filenames match the ones in the workflow **exactly**.\n\n*   **Base Model (LTXV 2.3 FP8):** Place this file in `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`.\n*   **LoRA:** Place the distilled LoRA file in `ComfyUI/models/loras/`.\n*   **Text Encoders (Gemma-3 & LTX-2.3 Projection):** Both files go into `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/`.\n*   **VAE (Video & Audio):** Both VAE files belong in the `ComfyUI/models/vae/` folder.\n*   **Upscale Model (x2):** This file goes into the `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models/` folder. \n\n*Tip: After moving the files, restart ComfyUI (or press the \"Refresh\" button in the UI) so the models can be loaded properly.*"
